'''馬克·尚德'''（{{lang-en|'''Mark Roland Shand'''}}，{{bd|1951年|6月28日|2014年|4月23日|catIdx=Shand}}），是一名英国旅游作家，<ref>{{cite web|title=The Elephant Man|url=http://www.wmagazine.com/parties/2008/03/mark_shand/|publisher=wmagazine|date=March 2008|accessdate=14 April 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607194839/http://www.wmagazine.com/parties/2008/03/mark_shand|archive-date=2013-06-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Duchess of Cornwall Background|url=http://www.royal.gov.uk/thecurrentroyalfamily/theduchessofcornwall/theduchessofcornwall.aspx|publisher=royal.gov.uk|accessdate=14 April 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307041814/http://www.royal.gov.uk/ThecurrentRoyalFamily/TheDuchessofCornwall/TheDuchessofCornwall.aspx|archivedate=2014-03-07}}</ref>也是[[康沃爾公爵夫人卡蜜拉|康沃爾公爵夫人卡蜜拉]]的弟弟。他担任环保组织{{link-en|大象家族|Elephant Family}}的主席<ref>{{cite web|title=Elephant Family|url=http://www.elephantfamily.org/who-we-are/our-london-team/|publisher=elephantfamily.org|accessdate=14 April 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308060821/http://www.elephantfamily.org/who-we-are/our-london-team/|archivedate=2014-03-08}}</ref>。

2014年4月23日，他死于纽约市<ref name="BBC death">{{cite news|title=Duchess of Cornwall's brother Mark Shand dies in fall|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-27131635|accessdate=23 April 2014|newspaper=BBC Online|date=23 April 2014|archive-date=2021-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516220223/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-27131635|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

